PROJECTS

Novartis Data Science Challenge

Solution for HackerEarth Machine Learning/ Data Science Challenge Aim is to predict the 'MULTIPLE_OFFENSE' column using given features. Helpful for the company as you may predict hacking events in the future using information you have. Hence, enabling you to mitigate or completely stop the hack from happening thereby saving valuable data from falling into the wrong hands. Link: https://github.com/Sharan-Babu/Novartis-Data-Science-Challenge

PUBG Win Percentile Prediction

Predict Win percentage and rank of a PUBG Player given other features based on player's previous matches like 'assists' and 'kills' per match. Dataset obtained from Kaggle and model trained in Google Colab. Used Linear Regression for prediction after exploratory data analysis and feature engineering. Link: https://github.com/Sharan-Babu/PUBG-Win-Percentage-Prediction

Income Classification (API)

Used Logistic Regression to predict the income class of person based on given fields of information. Model Deployed using Flask and Heroku Used Logistic Regression to predict the income class of person based on given fields of information. Link: https://income-classification-model.herokuapp.com/

Public or Private College? Clustering

Using K Means algorithm to cluster data points into 2 classes - Private college or Public College. Link: https://github.com/Sharan-Babu/Public-or-Private-College-K-Means-Clustering

Employee Attrition HackerEarth Challenge

Solution for HackerEarth Machine Learning Challenge. Aim is to predict the 'Attrition_rate' of employees in a company based on given features.
